Click to add bookmark, and double click to manage bookmark. Assign any keyboard shortcut as you wish.

Because of the branding guidelines of the Chrome Web Store, I changed the name "Pure Google Bookmark" to "Shortcut for Google Bookmarks".

Note: Keyboard shortcut only active when you are focusing on the page itself.

@update in 1.2

Add an option page to specify keyboard shortcut and window behavior.

@update in 1.2.1

Remove duplicated onRequest in background.html.
